-- PPF and KKCG May Bring KHL to Prague’s O2 Arena, MF Dnes Says
-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 2012-02-10T08:56:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-10/ppf-and-kkcg-may-bring-khl-to-prague-s-o2-arena-mf-dnes-says.html
PPF AS and KKCG, private equity
groups based in central and eastern  Europe , are considering
bringing the Kontinental Hockey League to  Prague ’s O2 Arena, 
Mlada Fronta  reported, without saying where it got its
information.  PPF and KKCG, creditors of the indebted O2 Arena operator
Bestsport, have to present a proposal of how to reorganize
Bestsport debt and revive its business to court in Prague by the
end of the week, the newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague at 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  